description: Love is spread through food and the world needs to feel the love. This skill gives you a random country from around the world to help you decide what to eat or cook tonight? Don't want to get Chinese again tonight? Maybe Alexa recommends Lebanese!
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask world food i want to eat somewhere else
Alexa, ask world food im feeling global
Alexa, ask world food lets try something new
name: World food
shortDescription: Want to try some new food from a different country but can't think of a country? Let alexa find you a great country to eat from.
